Addressing this predicament of the consumers and the banks is crucial as it is instrumental in speeding up the loan approval process. 
Based on the customer's background, identifying whether a specific customer will default a particular loan is the crux of the problem.
Consumer background includes assessing the consumer profile through information pertaining to their employment status, income, marital status, to name a few. 
Additionally, banks are working diligently with the credit department and investing many resources to eventually identify borrowers posing a credit risk to 
steer clear of losses.
